El diseño se completa con un cinturón ancho en raso o satén, y a menudo se acompaña de accesorios discretos, como zapatos de tacón alto en el mismo color, joyería elegante y un peinado recogido.Este diseño de vestido es perfecto para ocasiones especiales como bodas, galas o eventos formales, donde se busca un look sofisticado y clásico. La belleza atemporal del diseño de vestido corte Francés lo hace una elección perfecta para aquellos que buscan una pieza que nunca pase de moda.

Our "zoo" also has a big black bear, and that's my dad.My dad loves to sing,  He's also like Paddington Bear, fond of honey. Honey cake in the morning, honey biscuits at noon, and perhaps a cup of honey water in the evening. My dad is a brave bear who likes to take me and my brother to explore nature. We search for ants' homes in rock crevices, climb trees to pick the biggest, reddest oranges, and run and jump on the hillside. He always brings us surprises and fuels our curiosity.  We also have a magic-performing raccoon at home, and that's my mom. She loves cleanliness, turning the messiest room and dirtiest clothes neat and clean.
